title: Fajã dos Asnos
body: Located in the parish of Câmara de Lobos, on the lower part of Cabo Girão, it is also known as Fajã do Gregorio. It is partially cultivated, and the rocks that border it to the north are abundant with Helichrysum Monizii, a species that is hardly found in other parts of the island.

Câmara de Lobos: Fajã dos Asnos, Fajã do Gregorio
